# [GAIA](../wg/gaia.html)

## Summary

The GAIA working group met at IETF 126 to discuss rural backhaul design, community network lifecycle modeling, human-centric methodology in networking research, open fiber data mapping tools, and operational practices for circular device management. The session featured five presentations, detailed architectural discussions on network sustainability, and updates on the group's adopted draft.

